des: This is a fun trivia quiz game to test how big of a F.R.I.E.N.D.S fan you really are..! This quiz consist of 10 questions and provides you with 4 choices of answer. And at the end you get a score, based on your answers.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
